    <abstract>
      <t>   This document defines a hash polarization mitigation extension for
   Link Aggregation (LAG) and Equal-Cost Multi-Path (ECMP) routing.
   This document specifies hash input field selection rules, Shift
   Factor definition and generation methods, hash value adjustment
   algorithms, and normative requirements for device processing
   procedures.

